OL,4,CChildren 'held in solitary confinement'
OL,5, At least 40 children have been held in
OL,6, solitary confinement in young offenders
OL,7, institutions in the past year, the
OL,8, Victoria Derbyshire show has been told.
OL,10,FThe UN defines solitary confinement as
OL,11,Fbeing held for 22 hours a day without
OL,12,Fmeaningful human contact.
OL,14,FThe government said child prisoners
OL,15,Fwere never held in solitary confinement
OL,16,Fin England and Wales.
OL,18,FBut the Howard League for Penal Reform
OL,19,Fsaid it has been told of numerous
OL,20,Fincidents which amounted to it.
